  "en": [
    {
      "start": 60,
      "text": "If I was in love with an innocent person"
    },
    {
      "start": 66,
      "text": "I would not fully trust him"
    },
    {
      "start": 120,
      "text": "If love forgets, tears don't want to fall"
    },
    {
      "start": 128,
      "text": "Let those happiness be my guide"
    },
    {
      "start": 134,
      "text": "If love understands, promise to stay home"
    },
    {
      "start": 140,
      "text": "Can't give me, please finish it"
    },
    {
      "start": 148,
      "text": "I said I forgot, I didn't understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 152,
      "text": "That's because I love too much, I understand"
    },
    {
      "start": 155,
      "text": "I laughed, I forgave, I did it for you"
    },
    {
      "start": 161,
      "text": "With your happiness, tell me"
    },
    {
      "start": 165,
      "text": "Now let go of both hands, right"
    },
    {
      "start": 168,
      "text": "Don't care how much I can't bear"
    },
    {
